Class Pacient

java.lang.Object
vet.system1.Pacient
public class Pacient extends Object
Represents a patient in the veterinary system. A patient is an animal with a lot of details.

      public Pacient(int idAnimal, String numeAnimal, String gen, int varsta, String categorie, String rasa, String numeStapan, String numarTelefonStapan, String emailStapan)
      Constructs a Pacient with all the necessary details.
      Parameters:
      idAnimal - The ID of the animal.
      numeAnimal - The name of the animal.
      gen - The gender of the animal.
      varsta - The age of the animal.
      categorie - The category of the animal (e.g., dog, cat).
      rasa - The breed of the animal.
      numeStapan - The name of the animal's owner.
      numarTelefonStapan - The phone number of the animal's owner.
      emailStapan - The email address of the animal's owner.
